{"tha-ap304:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap304:0.2":"Padumakesaravagga ","tha-ap304:0.3":"Sabbagandhiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap304:1.1":"“Gandhamalam maya dinnam, ","tha-ap304:1.2":"vipassissa mahesino; ","tha-ap304:1.3":"Adasim ujubhutassa, ","tha-ap304:1.4":"koseyyavatthamuttamam. ","tha-ap304:2.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap304:2.2":"yam vatthamadadim pure; ","tha-ap304:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap304:2.4":"gandhadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap304:3.1":"Ito pannarase kappe, ","tha-ap304:3.2":"sucelo nama khattiyo; ","tha-ap304:3.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap304:3.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap304:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap304:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap304:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap304:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sabbagandhiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap304:6.1":"Sabbagandhiyattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}